c: 5
v: 19
t: "Enywe Abandu beshitabu, toto Omurumwa wefu yamala okhubeetsela, abeenosilie ebise biabarumwa bandi bawumao, muletsa okhuboola mbu; “Omwikanyilisi nohomba omubooli wamacheni amalayi shiyakhwitsila tawe” Toto yabetsela omulachilisi wamalayi omwikanjilisi, ne Nyasaye ni Omunyali wabuli eshindu"